---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import { SITE_DESCRIPTION, SITE_TITLE } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main>
			<h1>CloudSecure Research Blog</h1>
			<p>
				Welcome! My name is Alex McCarthy, and I am conducting research on behalf of <strong>CloudSecure</strong>.
			</p>
			<p>
				This blog documents my ongoing work in security automation, red teaming, and AI-driven vulnerability detection. Here you'll find technical write-ups, prototype designs, and reflections on building tools to help secure cloud environments and developer workflows.
			</p>
			<p>
				Recent topics include:
				<ul>
					<li>Automated security scanning and notifications</li>
					<li>Integrating AI models for code analysis</li>
					<li>Red team prototype development</li>
					<li>Exploring new cloud security technologies</li>
				</ul>
			</p>
			<p>
				Browse the <a href="/blog">blog</a> for daily updates, technical deep-dives, and project progress. If you have questions or want to collaborate, feel free to reach out!
			</p>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>
